<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>รายการพัสดุแผนกบริการเครื่องมือแพทย์</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
<style>
:root{
  --primary:#1a56db;--primary-dark:#1e429f;--primary-light:#e8f0fe;
  --success:#10b981;--warning:#f59e0b;--danger:#ef4444;--info:#6366f1;
  --bg:#f0f4f8;--card:#fff;--border:#e2e8f0;
  --text:#1e293b;--text-muted:#64748b;
  --sidebar-w:260px;--header-h:64px;
  --shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08),0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
  --shadow-md:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.10);--radius:12px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Sarabun',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-size:14px}
#app{display:flex;height:100vh;overflow:hidden}
#sidebar{width:var(--sidebar-w);background:linear-gradient(160deg,#1e429f 0%,#1a56db 60%,#1d4ed8 100%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;flex-shrink:0;height:100vh;overflow-y:auto;box-shadow:3px 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15);z-index:100}
#sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}#sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:4px}
.sidebar-header{padding:20px 16px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12)}
.sidebar-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:4px}
.logo-icon{width:38px;height:38px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.sidebar-logo h1{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.3}
.sidebar-sub{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-top:2px;padding-left:48px}
.sidebar-section{padding:8px 0}
.sidebar-section-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;padding:0 16px 6px}
.nav-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;margin:1px 8px;transition:all .2s;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;position:relative}
.nav-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:#fff}
.nav-item.active{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);color:#fff;font-weight:600}
.nav-item.active::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:3px;height:60%;background:#fff;border-radius:2px}
.nav-item .nav-icon{width:20px;text-align:center;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0}
.sidebar-footer{margin-top:auto;padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-size:11px}
#main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
#topbar{height:var(--header-h);background:var(--card);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 24px;gap:12px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06);flex-shrink:0;z-index:50}
#topbar .page-title{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);flex:1}
#topbar .page-subtitle{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:400;display:block}
#content{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:20px 24px}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;transition:all .2s;white-space:nowrap}
.btn-primary{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--primary-dark);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(26,86,219,.3)}
.btn-danger{background:var(--danger);color:#fff}.btn-danger:hover{background:#dc2626}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--primary);border:1.5px solid var(--primary)}.btn-outline:hover{background:var(--primary-light)}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--text-muted);border:1.5px solid var(--border)}.btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text)}
.btn-sm{padding:5px 11px;font-size:12px;border-radius:6px}.btn-icon{padding:7px;min-width:auto}
.stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px}
.stat-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;border:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
.stat-card:hover{border-color:var(--primary);box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(26,86,219,.13);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.stat-card:hover .stat-value{color:var(--primary)}
.stat-card:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.stat-icon{width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0}
.stat-icon.blue{background:#eff6ff;color:#2563eb}.stat-icon.green{background:#ecfdf5;color:#059669}
.stat-icon.orange{background:#fff7ed;color:#d97706}.stat-icon.purple{background:#f5f3ff;color:#7c3aed}
.stat-info .stat-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:4px}
.stat-info .stat-value{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);line-height:1}
.stat-info .stat-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:4px}
.stat-card .stat-hint{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.stat-card:hover .stat-hint{opacity:1}
.chart-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px}
.chart-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.chart-card.full{grid-column:1/-1}
.chart-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.sheet-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(175px,1fr));gap:14px}
.sheet-card{background:var(--card);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:18px 16px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .22s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.sheet-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),#6366f1);opacity:0;transition:opacity .22s}
.sheet-card:hover{border-color:var(--primary);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(26,86,219,.15)}
.sheet-card:hover::before{opacity:.06}
.sheet-card:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.sc-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:4px;transition:all .22s}
.sheet-card:hover .sc-icon{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}
.sc-count{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);line-height:1}
.sc-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.sc-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted)}
.sc-arrow{position:absolute;right:14px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--border);font-size:16px;transition:all .22s}
.sheet-card:hover .sc-arrow{color:var(--primary);right:10px}
.bar-chart{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.bar-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;padding:2px 4px;margin:-2px -4px;transition:background .15s}
.bar-item:hover{background:rgba(99,102,241,.06)}
.bar-item:hover .bar-label{color:var(--primary)}
.bar-label{width:150px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;flex-shrink:0;text-align:right}
.bar-track{flex:1;background:var(--bg);border-radius:20px;height:22px;overflow:hidden}
.bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:20px;transition:width 1s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);display:flex;align-items:center;padding-left:10px}
.bar-val{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap}
.donut-wrap{display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.donut-legend{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;flex:1;min-width:140px}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;padding:5px 8px;border-radius:8px;transition:background .15s;margin:-5px -8px}
.legend-item:hover{background:var(--primary-light)}
.legend-item:hover span{color:var(--primary)}
.legend-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.donut-slice{cursor:pointer;transition:opacity .2s;outline:none}
.donut-slice:hover{opacity:.75}
.toolbar{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px 16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;align-items:center}
.search-box{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex:1;min-width:200px;background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 12px}
.search-box i{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:13px}
.search-box input{border:none;background:transparent;outline:none;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;flex:1;color:var(--text)}
.filter-select{background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 12px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.export-group{display:flex;gap:6px}
.search-mode-toggle{display:flex;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;flex-shrink:0}
.search-mode-btn{padding:6px 11px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-muted);border:none;font-family:inherit;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
.search-mode-btn:last-child{border-right:none}
.search-mode-btn.active{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}
.search-mode-btn:hover:not(.active){background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.search-highlight{background:#fef08a;border-radius:2px;padding:0 1px}
.table-container{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.table-header{padding:14px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0}
.table-header h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}
.record-count{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);background:var(--bg);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px}
.table-wrap{overflow:auto;flex:1;max-height:calc(100vh - 310px)}
.table-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar{height:6px;width:6px}
.table-wrap::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#cbd5e1;border-radius:4px}
table{width:max-content;min-width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px}
thead th{padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-muted);border-bottom:2px solid var(--border);white-space:nowrap;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:20;background:#f8fafc;box-shadow:inset 0 -2px 0 var(--border)}
thead th:hover{color:var(--primary);background:#f1f5f9}
thead th.sorted{color:var(--primary)}
thead th .si{margin-left:4px;opacity:.3;font-size:10px}
thead th.sorted .si{opacity:1}
thead th:first-child,tbody td:first-child{position:sticky;left:0;z-index:15;background:inherit}
thead th:first-child{z-index:25;background:#f8fafc}
tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;transition:background .12s}
tbody tr:hover{background:#f8fafc}
tbody tr:hover td:first-child{background:#f8fafc}
tbody td{padding:9px 14px;color:var(--text);max-width:220px;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:middle}
.td-actions{display:flex;gap:5px;white-space:nowrap}
.status-badge{display:inline-block;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
.st-good{background:#dcfce7;color:#15803d}
.st-wait{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e}
.st-done{background:#fee2e2;color:#b91c1c}
.st-broken{background:#fde8d8;color:#c2410c}
.st-s{background:#f3e8ff;color:#7e22ce}
.st-other{background:#f1f5f9;color:#64748b}
.pagination{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0}
.pagination .info{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)}
.page-btns{display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center}
.page-btn{width:32px;height:32px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-muted);background:var(--card);transition:all .2s;user-select:none}
.page-btn:hover:not(.dis){border-color:var(--primary);color:var(--primary)}
.page-btn.active{background:var(--primary);border-color:var(--primary);color:#fff}
.page-btn.dis{opacity:.35;cursor:not-allowed;pointer-events:none}
.page-size-sel{font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:4px 8px;background:var(--card);color:var(--text);outline:none;cursor:pointer}
.modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);z-index:999;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .2s}
.modal-overlay.show{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
.modal{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);width:100%;max-width:780px;max-height:92vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.22);transform:scale(.95);transition:transform .2s}
.modal-overlay.show .modal{transform:scale(1)}
.modal-header{padding:18px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}
.modal-header h2{font-size:16px;font-weight:700}
.modal-close{background:none;border:none;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-muted);padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px}
.modal-close:hover{background:var(--bg)}
.modal-body{padding:20px 24px;overflow-y:auto;flex:1}
.modal-body::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px}.modal-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#cbd5e1;border-radius:4px}
.modal-footer{padding:14px 24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;flex-shrink:0}
.form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px}
.form-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.form-group.full{grid-column:1/-1}
.form-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.badge-dd{font-size:10px;background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600}
.plain-input{width:100%;padding:9px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);outline:none;transition:border .2s;background:var(--bg)}
.plain-input:focus{border-color:var(--primary);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(26,86,219,.08)}
.combo-wrap{position:relative}
.combo-wrap input{width:100%;padding:9px 36px 9px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);outline:none;transition:border .2s;background:var(--bg)}
.combo-wrap input:focus{border-color:var(--primary);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(26,86,219,.08)}
.combo-wrap .dd-arrow{position:absolute;right:10px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--text-muted);font-size:11px;pointer-events:none}
.dd-list{position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 2px);left:0;right:0;background:#fff;border:1.5px solid var(--primary);border-radius:8px;max-height:200px;overflow-y:auto;z-index:1000;box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);display:none}
.dd-list.open{display:block}
.dd-list::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}.dd-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#cbd5e1;border-radius:4px}
.dd-item{padding:8px 12px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:background .1s;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9}
.dd-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.dd-item:hover,.dd-item.hl{background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.dd-empty{padding:10px 12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12px;text-align:center}
#loading{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,.88);z-index:9999;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:16px}
.spinner{width:44px;height:44px;border:4px solid #e2e8f0;border-top-color:var(--primary);border-radius:50%;animation:spin 1s linear infinite}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
#toast-wrap{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:9998;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.toast{background:var(--text);color:#fff;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:10px;font-size:13px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;animation:slideIn .3s ease;max-width:320px}
.toast.success{background:var(--success)}.toast.error{background:var(--danger)}
@keyframes slideIn{from{transform:translateX(110%);opacity:0}to{transform:translateX(0);opacity:1}}
#status-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.55);z-index:998;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .2s}
#status-overlay.show{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
#status-modal{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);width:100%;max-width:1100px;max-height:92vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.25);transform:scale(.95);transition:transform .2s}
#status-overlay.show #status-modal{transform:scale(1)}
.sm-header{padding:18px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-shrink:0}
.sm-badge{padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700}
.sm-count{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-left:auto;background:var(--bg);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px}
.sm-body{overflow-y:auto;flex:1}
.sm-body::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px}.sm-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#cbd5e1;border-radius:4px}
.sm-table-wrap{overflow-x:auto}
.sm-search{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin:14px 20px;background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 12px}
.sm-search i{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:13px}
.sm-search input{border:none;background:transparent;outline:none;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;flex:1}
.sm-sheet-tag{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary);margin-right:4px;white-space:nowrap}
.sm-footer{padding:14px 24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-shrink:0}
.sm-page-info{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)}
.empty-state{text-align:center;padding:80px 24px;color:var(--text-muted)}
.empty-state i{font-size:48px;opacity:.4;margin-bottom:16px}
.empty-state h3{font-size:18px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:700}
.empty-state p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 16px}
.empty-state code{background:var(--bg);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;color:var(--primary)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:14px">กำลังโหลดข้อมูล...</div></div>
<div id="toast-wrap"></div>

<div id="app">
  <nav id="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-header">
      <div class="sidebar-logo">
        <div class="logo-icon"><i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i></div>
        <h1>ระบบพัสดุ<br>เครื่องมือแพทย์</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-sub">แผนกบริการเครื่องมือแพทย์</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-section-label">ภาพรวม</div>
      <div class="nav-item active" onclick="showDashboard()" id="nav-dashboard">
        <span class="nav-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i></span><span>Dashboard</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="sidebar-section-label">รายการพัสดุ</div>
      <div id="sheet-nav-list"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-footer">
      <div><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Powered by Supabase</div>
      <div style="margin-top:4px;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4">รายการพัสดุแผนกบริการเครื่องมือแพทย์</div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div id="main">
